snippet.title: Strawberry Shortcake - Musical Match-ups (Atari 2600)
snippet.description:
Video games have come a berry long way! Check out Strawberry's video game debut from 1983.
You can play the game now in your browser at archive.org - click this link: http://bit.ly/1iHxXB0

Visit Strawberry online at http://www.strawberryshortcake.com/
Berry fun mobile apps! http://appstore.com/strawberryshortcake
Purchase Strawberry DVDs at http://amzn.to/1WSa0WM and Digital HD copies! http://apple.co/1OEPWIl
Full episodes on Netflix! http://bit.ly/berrybitty
Friend Strawberry on Facebook! http://www.facebook.com/StrawberryShortcake #StrawberryShortcake #WildBrain
